name: Transgenic_Sample_Eleven
content:
Transgenic Sample Eleven was the name given by Sannus Lorrick to a Vorantikus that he infected with Rakghoul plague during his experiments on Ord Mantell. In 3639 BBY a strike team stormed Lorrick's lab and neutralized all threats within, including the Transgenic Sample Eleven.
Transgenic Sample Eleven appears in the Star Wars: The Old Republic as a boss during the flashpoint "Lost Island".
